title: Double trouble, 2 bed 2 bath here at Aventino
posting_body: ['Aventino Apartments', '200 Winchester Circle, Los Gatos, CA, 95032', 'Want more information?', 'Follow this link:', '<URL> call us at--', 'show contact info', '11', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact our team.', 'Modern European Living in the Heart of Silicon Valley', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1123 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'At Aventino it’s all about comfort, convenience, and community.', 'We boast a wide selection of studio, 1, and 2 bedroom apartments with spacious open floor plans full of luxury finishes.', 'Enjoy European style cabinetry, wood flooring, stainless steel appliances, plush carpeting, and modern detailing throughout your homes.', 'Fido’s even welcome to join your new adventure in our pet-friendly community!', 'The comfort and convenience doesn’t stop at your home, Aventino offers residents abundant community amenities.', 'Take advantage of beautiful indoor and outdoor personal fitness options including a resort style lap pool and spa, fitness center, and yoga studio.', 'The community’s private access to the Los Gatos Creek Trail is a perfect way to start or end your day with a hike.', 'Our updated resident lounge includes a business center, conference room, and game room where you can join friends for a movie, or a game of pool.', 'Start a new adventure with Aventino today, contact us and schedule a personalized tour to find your perfect fit!', 'Features', '- Carpet', '- Walk', 'In Closets', '- Internet Access', '- Dishwasher', '- Washer Dryer', 'In Unit', '- Alarm System', '- Patio or Balcony', '- Cable or Satellite', 'Community Amenities', '- Zen Yoga Studio', '- Fit Gym w/ Cardio & Weights', '- Close Proximity to Downtown Los Gatos & Shops', '- Kids Playground', '- Co-working Space w/ WiFi Access', '- Relaxing Pool, Spa & Sun Terrace', '- Easy Freeway Access to Hwy 85/17/280', '- Direct Access to Los Gatos Creek Trail', '- Outdoor BBQ Grilling Station', '- Private Movie Screening Room', 'qSFcSVvE9']
